ivardefs.name: active
ivardefs.desc: Whether this related person record is in active use.

ivardefs.name: address_
ivardefs.desc: Address where the related person can be contacted or visited.

ivardefs.name: birthDate
ivardefs.desc: The date on which the related person was born.

ivardefs.name: communication_
ivardefs.desc: A language which may be used to communicate with about the patient's health.

ivardefs.name: gender
ivardefs.desc: Administrative Gender - the gender that the person is considered to have for administration and record keeping purposes.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Identifier for a person within a particular scope.

ivardefs.name: name_
ivardefs.desc: A name associated with the person.

ivardefs.name: patient
ivardefs.desc: The patient this person is related to.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: The period of time during which this relationship is or was active. If there are no dates defined, then the interval is unknown.

ivardefs.name: relationship_
ivardefs.desc: The nature of the relationship between a patient and the related person.

ivardefs.name: telecom_
ivardefs.desc: A contact detail for the person, e.g. a telephone number or an email address.

properties.desc: Information about a person that is involved in the care for a patient, but who is not the target of healthcare, nor has a formal responsibility in the care process.
